{"type": "article", "id": 27291, "title": "智能测醉器", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-25T06:32:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070214400192vNZ3GAuKVx8gBI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>小酌或者应酬后想了解自己的身体状况？来自美国的 Edge Tech Labs 希望通过这款世界上最小的酒精测量仪 DrinkMate 让这个过程变得方便又卫生。它的进气口经过特殊设计，可以将呼出的气体精准地引导至内置的感应器中，免去了口腔的直接接触。使用时只需要把它插入手机（这也是它的电力来源），对着它轻轻吹一口气，配套的软件就会显示出血液酒精浓度（BAC）。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/drinkmate-the-miniature-smartphone-breathalyzer#/\">链接</a>购买这个小巧的测醉器，售价为 35 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143959TQqHFluLm62BVi5D.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021439596kHyMeTN1O8BDvQ7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144000OA92y34rBKHmniMt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59347181\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144000yVj8lGqFH4DQepXd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}